lead_paragraph: Carrying identification documents and bitterness over their sudden joblessness, hundreds of ex-casino workers began filing for unemployment Wednesday morning, the first attendees at an assistance center that expects to process 5,000 newly laid-off workers over the next three days.

headline.main: Casino Closures Brings Mass Unemployment Filing
headline.print_headline: Casino Closures Brings Mass Unemployment Filing
